Rating: 4
I love this recipe! It is easy to make but it looks super fancy. Next time I would probably leave out the cardamom or maybe try to substitute it with cinnamon. The fruit in California is so sweet that you probably don't need to add anything.

Rating: 3
My guests loved this recipe. I couldn't find peach ice cream so substituted peach frozen yogurt, less fat and just as delicious. Very easy to make.